Theorem (15.18): - 0 = 0
Proof:
    - 0 = 0
  =⟨ “Additive identity” ⟩
    0 + - 0 = 0
  =⟨ “Unary minus” ⟩
    0 = 0 — This is “Reflexivity of =”
